<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      xmlns:py="http://genshi.edgewall.org/"
      xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
      lang="en">

<xi:include href="master.xml" />

<head>
  <title>Realm Linux Management Tools</title>
</head>
<body>

  <h2>Message</h2>  

  <div class="message">
    <p py:content="message" />
  </div>

  <p>If you are having a problem with the Realm Linux Management Tools, or
    perhaps feel as if the Liquid Dragon wont let you near the treasure,
    please create a support ticket by emailing 
    <a href="mailto:linux@help.ncsu.edu">linux@help.ncsu.edu</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>Authorization Information</h2>

  <p>Greetings, ${fullname}.  You are user "${userid}".</p>

  <p>You are a member of the following ACLs:</p>
  <ul py:if="len(acls) > 0">
    <li py:for="acl in acls" py:content="acl"/>
  </ul>
  <p py:if="len(acls) == 0">
    You have no ACL memberships.
  </p>

</body>

</html>

